{"tid":85770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死5隻]大貨車炮彈式撞塌民房　至少5死","createTime":"2017-01-18T14:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T06:19:46.000Z","uid":32407,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0498017ae76ec96ac2c5e51bb0b6c1e297eb3445","tid":85770,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170117/photo/bkncn-20170117181515385-0117_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170117%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170117181515385-0117_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=bd9eedb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=ivu1EHg7zyOx%2Bwb3cawZBksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d9e03914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 寧夏中衞市海原縣今日中午12時許發生一宗恐怖車禍，一輛大貨車如炮彈般將一排民房撞毀，造成多幢民房倒塌，迅即變成廢墟。目前救援人員仍在現場進行搜救，當地相關部門正統計具體傷亡情況，據指事故造成至少包括大貨車司機在內5人死亡，另有3人受傷送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n從閉路電視畫面所見，一輛大貨車於中午12時46分高速撞向路邊的多幢民房，將民房推倒，並揚起大量灰塵。事發後，現場一片狼藉，到處都是殘磚斷瓦。多輛救護車趕抵現場，另有多名消防員及村民持挖掘工具，在瓦礫堆中搜救被埋者。<br />\n<br />\n網絡流傳司機當場死亡，而現場發現了多名死者的遺體，並由棉被蓋住，家屬在旁痛哭。至於事發原因，網傳肇事大貨車當時載有大量沙石，因失控撞向民居，另有指大貨車是煞車失靈肇禍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d97b931e2677e4ac4e24b5d08e5e2bcbda92b74","tid":85770,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"日本車vs豆腐渣"},{"pid":"ebc00744644bc85a11234e73919fde002e2aa98f","tid":85770,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e9b6f7c51f4695e79ba25801395af0480e499d8","tid":85770,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj